# Session-scratch planning artifacts. These are written by the agent
# during a working session as ephemeral notes — never committed.
# Living in the repo root makes them easy to grep but also easy to
# accidentally `git add .`; gitignore both belt-and-braces.
NEXT_SESSION.md
RECOMMENDATION.md
DOCS_STALE_PUNCHLIST.md
DESIGN.md

# Generated artifacts (built from scripts/build_deck.py, scripts/gen_exec_brief.py)
agora_deck.pdf
docs/*.docx
